snippet.title: Uncharted: Legacy of Thieves Collection - PC Pre-Purchase Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for Uncharted: Legacy of Thieves Collection, coming to PC October 19th, 2022 on Epic Games Store and Steam. This Uncharted game collection features UNCHARTED 4: A Thief’s End and UNCHARTED: The Lost Legacy, previously exclusive to just the PlayStation 4.

#IGN #Uncharted #UnchartedLegacyOfThieves
